CELL 0.71073 24.4632 8.0039 8.1963 90 99.745 90
ZERR 4 0.0015 0.0004 0.0005 0 0.002 0
LATT 7
SYMM -X,+Y,0.5-Z
SFAC C H Br N Pb
UNIT 24 68 16 8 4
SADI C N1 N1 C0AA
SADI C C2 C2 C0AA
SADI C4A C2 C2 C4
